Package: dmdr
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Mode Decomposition
Version: 0.1.0
Authors: Julia Worthington <julia.worthington@colorado.edu>
Description: This package executes the dynamic mode decomposition (DMD) algorithm
    of raw data and plots the resulting modes, underlying dynamics, and eigenvalues.
    It also approximates the original data using the DMD. See 
    <https://github.com/juliaeworthington/dmdr> for examples and updates.
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    ggforce,
    ggplot2,
    patchwork,
    pracma,
    RColorBrewer
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/juliaeworthington/dmdr
BugReports: https://github.com/juliaeworthington/dmdr/issues
